  <brief_title>Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Efficacy and the Safety of Antihypertensive Tablets</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 8-Week, Randomized, Double-blind, Parallel Designed, Phase II Multi-center Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Antihypertensive Efficacy and the Safety of OJP-2028 Tablets in Patients With the Uncomplicated Essential Hypertension</official_title>
