  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the optimal dosage of the clinical trial which is
      evaluating the antihypertensive efficacy and the safety of OJP-2028 tablets in patients with
      the uncomplicated essential hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Evaluating the antihypertensive efficacy and the safety of OJP-2028 tablets in patients with
      the uncomplicated essential hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
