  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Adult men and women (Age 18-75 years)

          2. Uncomplicated essential hypertension: Clinic sitting SiDBP between 90 and 109 mmHg
             after 2 week placebo run-in period

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Secondary hypertension

          2. History and/or signs of cardiovascular complications (eg; myocardial infarction,
             unstable angina)

          3. Pregnancy or lactation

          4. Contraindications to the antihypertensive drugs to be used during the treatment period
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
